quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,"Ndee ko Simoore Men Tellinii nde, Men wajimmbini gollirgol √Ďaawooje mayre, Men Tellini e mayre Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe; joortagol wonnde on waajitorta ko woni kon e nder mayre immorde e √Ďaawooje …óen koni ngollironnde."
  24,2,"Debbo jeenoowo e gorko jinoowo jiwo e suka piyee gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe paatawol teemedere, wata newaare e yurmeende nanngu on haa ronkon √Īimnude e ma…ď…ďe hiddi ndin maa…óun newinanon …ďe …óum, si tawii on laatiki hi…óon gom…óini Alla e √Ďalaande Laakara nden, yo tawe √Īimnugol hiddi ndin e ma…ď…ďe jamaa gom…óin…ďe …ďen fii kempinngol lollinngol fii ma…ď…ďe, e ha…óirgol kam…ďe …ói…óo tanaa ma…ď…ďe."
  24,3,"Ka hul…ďinngol fii jeeno Alla jaŇčtii wonnde on gaadarii…óo …óum o rer…óantaa fii resugol si wanaa debbo jinoowo wano makko maa…óum sirkoowo mo rentotaako e jina wonndude e waasude dagagol resugol mo, on debbo wowtinii…óo jeeno o rer…óan- taa reseede si wanaa gorko jinoowo wano makko maa…óum sirkoowo mo rentotaako hurum jom galle makko, na harminaa e dow gom…óin…ďe …ďen resugol debbo jinoowo on e resinngol gorko jInoowo on."
  24,4,"E …ďen …ďe no werloo ko pankare e sonnaa…ďe nantii…ďe …ďen, (e wor…ďe reenii…ďe …ďen wano sonnaa-…ďe …ďen non), refti hara …ďe addaali seedee…ďe nayo e dow ko …ďe werlii kon e ma…ď…ďe immorde e bonki haray piyee …ďe -an √Īaawoowo on- paatawol cappan…óe jeetati, wata on ja…ďan …ďe seedeeyaagal poomaa. Ko …ďen …óon woni tukkude nantii…ďe …ďen, ko kam…ďe woni yaltu…ďe …ďen e gaayi doftaare Alla nden."
  24,5,"Si wanaa …ďen tuubu…ďe ka Alla …ďaawo nden huunde nde …ďe wa…ói , …ďe mo∆ī∆īintini golle ma…ď…ďe, haray pellet, Alla ja…ďay tuubuubuyee ma…ď…ďe on e seedeeyaagal ma…ď…ďe ngal, pellet, Alla ko O Surroowo wonannde on tuubu…óo immorde e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, ko O Yurmetee…óo …ďe."
  24,6,"E …ďen wor…ďe tukkoo…ďe sonnaa…ďe mu'un hara alanaa …ďe seedee…ďe tanaa wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe …ďe no seedoo e dow sellugol ko …ďe tukkiri ko [sonnaa…ďe …ďen]; ko yo gooto [kala] e ma…ď…ďe seedo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla, pellet kanko, ko o goongu…óo e ko o tukkiri kon sonnaajo makko on immorde e jina."
  24,7,"Refti e nder seedagol makko jowa…ďol ngol o …ďeyda hu…óirgol wonkii makko jojjidugol e kuddi ndin si o laatike fenu…óu e ko o tukkire kon [sonnaajo on]."
  24,8,"Sakko [sonnaajo on] jojja sabu …óum hiddeede hiddi jeeno ngon, o martinira e makko ngol hiddegol, nde kanko o seedotoo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla: "Pellet [gorko on] ko o fenu…óo e ko o tukkiri mo kon."
  24,9,"Refti e nder seedagol makko jowa…ďol ngol o …ďeyda hu…óirgol wonkii makko kin tikkere Alla nden e dow makko si [gorko on] laatike goongu…óo e nder ko o tukkiri mo kon."
  24,10,"Sinndo wanaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon -onon yim…ďe …ďen- e Yurmeende Makko nden e moo…óon, e wonndema kadi Kank ko O ja…ďanoowo tuubuubuyee kala tuubu…óo immorde e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, ko O √Ďee√Īo ka fewjoore Makko e ka Sari'a Makko O yaccinanayno on Lepte …óen e dow bakkatuuji mo'on …óin, O wirtirayno on sabu majji."
  24,11,"Pellet, …ďen addu…ďe penaale …óen (…óum le ko tukkirgol bonki Yumma gom…óin…ďe …ďen Aa'isa yo Alla weltor mo) ko …ďe jamaa dammbitii…óo(askitiido) e moo…óon, -onon gom…óin…ďe …ďen- wata on sikku ko …ďe fefindii kon ko bone mo'on, ko woni, …óum ko mo∆ī∆īere sabu ko woni kon e mu'un immorde e mbarjaari e ndarndagol gom…óin…ďe …ďen, e ko jokki …óum kon e la…ď…ďinngol Yumma gom…óin…ďe …ďen. No woodani kala tawaa…óo e tukkirgol [NeenAa'isa] bonki njo…ďdi ko o faggitii kon immorde e junuubu sabu wowlugol makko ngol penaale …óen, e on fawtii…óo ko mawni kon e …óum sabu fu…ó…óagol makko …óum, no woodani mo Lepte maw…óe. Ko faandaa e …óum ko hooreejo naafiqii…ďe …ďen Abdullaahi bun Ubayyu bun Saluulu."
  24,12,"Ko haanunoo si wor…ďe gom…óin…ďe …ďen e rew…ďe gom…óin…ďe …ďen nanii …óee penaale maw…óe …ďe hooloo hisugol on mo …óum fenaa on e hoore-mu'un immorde e musi…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe gom…óin…ďe …ďen, …ďe wi'a: "∆äum ko fenaande …ďanngunde nii"."
  24,13,"Ko haanunoo ko nde fefindii…ďe …ďen e dow Yumma gom…óin…ďe …ďen Aa'isa yo Alla weltor mo addaynoo seedee…ďe nayo e dow ngol fefindagol ma…ď…ďe mawngol, …ďe seedoo e dow sellugol ko …ďe dammbi kon e makko, si tawii …ďe addaali seedee…ďe nayo e dow …óum -te …ďe addataa …ďe poomaa- haray kam…ďe ko …ďe fenoo…ďe ka √Ďaawoore Alla."
  24,14,"Sinndo wonaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon -onon gom…óin…ďe …ďen- e Yurmeende Makko nden e moo…óon nde tawnoo O yaccinantaa on Lepte …óen, O la…ď…ďini …ďen tuubu…ďe immorde e muu…óon; he…ďayno on Lepte maw…óe sabu ko ukki…óon kon e mu'un immorde e fenaande e fefindagol e dow Yumma gom…óin…ďe …ďen."
  24,15,"Tuma yoga ma…ď…ďe fillantoo nde yoga, hi…óon eggira nde kunndu…óe moo…óon wonndude e bonugol mayre; alanah on e …óum ganndal, hi…óon sikka wonnde …óum ko newii…óum, hara le …óum ko mawnu…óum ka Alla; sabu ko woni kon e mu'un immorde e fenaande e tukkugol laa…ďu…óo."
  24,16,"Ko haanunoo tuma nanu…óon ndee fenaande, wi'on: "Sellantaa men nde men wowlata oo fiyaake kaanu…óo, Senayee wonanii Ma Joomi amen, ndee huunde nde …ďe werlii …óum e Yumma gom…óin…ďe …ďen ko fenaande mawnde"."
  24,17,"Alla no anndintinnde on O laa…ďana on fii wata on fillito yeru ndee fenaande werlo…óon bonki e laa…ďu…óo, si tawii on laatike gom…óin…ďe Alla."
  24,18,"Alla no …ďannginannde on Aayeeje moftu…óe …óen √Ďaawooje Makko …óen e Waajuuji Makko …óin, Alla ko O Anndu…óo golle mon …óen, hay e huunde su…óanaaki e majje, aray O yo…ďa on e dow majje, ko O √Ďee√Īo ka Fewjoore Makko e ka Sari'a Makko."
  24,19,"Pellet, …ďen yi…óu…ďe yo pankare …óe lollu e hoore gom…óin…ďe …ďen -no jeyaa e majji tukkirgol jeeno ngon- no woodani …ďe Lepte muusu…óe ka aduna sabu √Īimnugol hiddi tukkugol e dow ma…ď…ďe, no woodani …ďe kadi ka Laakara Lepte Yiite, Alla no Anndi penaale ma…ď…ďe …óen, e ko fiyakuuji jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen wontata, hiMo Anndi kadi nafaaji ma…ď…ďe …óin, onon on anndah …óum."
  24,20,"Sinndo wonaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon -onon …ďee ukkii…ďe e penaale- e Yurmeende Makko nden e mo'on, sinndo wonaano pellet Alla ko O Newii…óo Hinnotoo…óo on, O yaccinanayno on Lepte …óen."
  24,21,"Ko onon yo …ďen gom…óin…ďe Alla golliri Sari'a Makko on, wata on jokku …óate Seytaane …óen sabu cu…óugol makko ngol meere nden, kala jokku…óo …óati makko …óin pellet, o yamiray mo ko kaani kon immorde e konngu…ói e kuu…óe, e ko sari'a on a√Īi kon, sinndo wonaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon -onon gom…óin…ďe …ďen- hay e gooto e mo'on laa…ďirtaano tuubuubuyee on poomaa hay o tuubi, kono Alla hiMo la…ď…ďinira on mo O Muuyi ja…ďanngol mo tuubuubuyee makko on, Alla ko O Nanoowo konngu…ói mo'on …óin, Anndu…óo golle mo'on …óen, hay e huunde e majje suu…óanaaki Mo, aray O yo…ďa on e dow majje."
  24,22,"Wata jom …ďural en ka Diina e jom yaajeende en ka jawdi woondu fii …óalugol okkugol …ďadondiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe hatonnjin…ďe …ďen, -sabu …ďillaare nde …ďe woni nden e mu'un, immorde e …ďen feru…ďe ka Laawol Alla- sabu junuubu mo …ďe wa…ó…óitii …óun, yo …ďe yaafano …ďe, …ďe yawtana…ďe. Kaa on yi…óah yo Alla yawtan on junubaaji mo'on …óin si on yaafanike …ďe on yawtii?! Alla ko O Surroowo wonannde on tuubu…óo immorde e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, ko O Yurmetee…óo …ďe, yo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen √Īentin Mo. O Aaya ko fii Abuu Bakri Asiddiiqi (yo Alla weltor mo) ngal Tellii tuma nde o woondunoo fii …óalugol nafkugol Mistahu sabu tawtugol makko pene …óen."
  24,23,"∆Āen tukkoo…ďe rew…ďe nantii…ďe welsindii…ďe e pankare …ďen, …ďen …ďe tawata miijo bonugol aratah e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe ra…óaama e yurmeende Alla nden aduna e laakara. No woodani …ďe lepte mawnu…óe laakara."
  24,24,"He…ďay …ďe …óen Lepte √Ďalnde Darngal, √Ďalnde seedoytoo e dow ma…ď…ďe …óen…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ko …ďe wowlirnoo …óe kon immorde e meere, seedoyoo e dow ma…ď…ďe kadi juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e koy…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen sabu ko …ďe laatinoo kon hi…ďe golla."
  24,25,"E nder ngal √Ďallal Alla huu…ďinanay …ďe njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin e Nun…óal, …ďe annda kadi pellet, Alla Senayee wonanii Mo ko Kanko woni Goonga, kala ko iwri e Makko immorde e kumpital maa…óum fodoore maa…óum kammbaa ko Goonga …ďannguka sikke alah e makka."
  24,26,"Kala ko so…ďi immorde ka wor…ďe e ka rew…ďe e ka konngu…ói e ka kuu…óe na yaadi ina hawri e kala huunde so…ďunde. Kala ko laa…ďi kon kadi immorde e …óum haray ko dammbondir…óum e hawrondir…óum e kala huunde laa…ďunde. ∆Āen wor…ďe laa…ďu…ďe e rew…ďe laa…ďu…ďe ko …ďe martinaa…ďe e ko wor…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen e rew…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen wowlata …ďe kon. No woodani …ďe haforaneede immorde ka Alla hiMo haforira …óum bakkatuuji ma…ď…ďe, no woodani …ďe arsike teddu…óo …óum le ko Aljanna on."
  24,27,"Ko onon yo gom…óin…ďe Alla golliri Sari'a Makko on, wata on naatu e cuu…ói …ói wonaa cuu…ói mo'on haa duŇčino…óon ho…óu…ďe …ďen e majji fii naatugol tawa …ďe, salminon e ma…ď…ďe, wi'on ka salminngol e ka duŇčinagol: "Kisiyee e moo…óun, yo mi naatu?" Ko ngol duŇčinagol ngol yamira…óon …óum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on diini naatugol juha. Bela jo'o on annditay ko yamira…óon kon …óofto…óon …óum."
  24,28,"Si on tawaali go…ó…óo e nder …óin cuu…ói, haray wata on naatu e majji haa duŇčanee on naatugol e majji immorde e …ďen jey…ďe duŇčayee(sakkitoore) on. Si jey…ďe …ói …ďen wi'anii on: (Ruttee) haray ruttee wata on naatu e majji, pellet, ko …óum …ďuri laa…ďannde on ka Alla, Alla non hiMo Anndi ko golloton hay e huunde e golle mo'on …óen suu…óanaaki Mo, aray O yo…ďa on e dow majje."
  24,29,"Junuubu fawaaki on si on naatii hara on duŇčinaaki e cuu…ói kafaa…ói …ói gooto hertoraa jeyal mu'um, heblanaa…ói fii ko nafa yim…ďe …ďen fow; wano birooji …óin e bitikaaji …óin ka maakitiiji, Alla no Anndi ko fe√Ī√Īinton immorde e golle mo'on e alhaaliiji mo'on e ko suu…óoton, hay huunde e …óum suu…óanaaki Mo, aray O yo…ďa on e dow mu'un."
  24,30,"Maakan -an Nulaa…óo- wor…ďe gom…óin…ďe …ďen yo …ďe hippu giti ma…ď…ďe …óen gaayi ndaarude e ko daganaki …ďe immorde e sonnaa…ďe e awraaji, …ďe reena farjuuji ma…ď…ďe immorde e yanugol e ko harminaa kon, e immorde e huncugol …óum, ngol hippugol gite gaayi e ndaarude faade e kon ko Alla harmini …ďurata la…ď…ďinnde on ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko O Humpitii…óo ko …ďe huuwata, hay e huunde e …óum suu…óanaaki Mo, aray O Yo…ďa …ďe e dow …óum."
  24,31,"Maakan rew…ďe gom…óin…ďe …ďen yo …ďe hippu gite ma…ď…ďe …óen gaayi ndaarude e ko daganaaki …ďe ndaarugol kon immorde e awraaji, …ďe reenira farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin wo…ó…óitagol pankare …óen e surrugol …ói, wata …ďe fe√Ī√Īinan cu…óaari ma…ď…ďe ndin janan…ďe …ďen si wanaa ko fee√Īi kon e mayri, kon ko newotaako suu…óugol …óum wano conci …óin, yo …ďe fawu tiggaaje ma…ď…ďe …óen e hoore jol…óe wontir…óe …óen ka senngo dow conci ma…ď…ďe fii yo …ďe suu…óu cukuli ma…ď…ďe …óin e geece ma…ď…ďe …óen e daa…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, wata …ďe fe√Ī√Īinan cu…óaari ma…ď…ďe suu…óiindi ndin si wanaa moodi…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, maa…óum baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, maa…óum baabiraa…ďe moodi…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, maa…óum …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, maa…óum …ďi…ó…ďe moodi…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, maa…óum musi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, maa…óum …ďi…ó…ďe musi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, maa…óum …ďi…ó…ďe banndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, maa…óum sonnaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe hoolaa…ďe …ďen, foti ko …ďe jul…ďe maa ko …ďe heefer…ďe, maa…óum …ďen …ďe …ďe jeyi immorde e maccu…ďe maa…óum hor…ďe, maa…óum wor…ďe jokkoo…ďe √Īiiri …ďe maraa haaju e rew…ďe, maa…óum booboo…ďe …ďe humpitaaki …ďen awraaji sonnaa…ďe sabu fam…óugol ma…ď…ďe, wata sonnaa…ďe …ďen fiyandir koy…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen faadagol fii yo annde ko …ďe suu…ói kon immorde e cuu…óaari ma…ď…ďe yeru li…ďe e ko nanndi e …óum. Tuubee rutto…óon ka Alla no fotu…óon fodde -ko onon yo gom…óin…ďe- tijjagol on he…ďay ko …óa…ď…ďaa kon, da…óon ko hulaa kon."
  24,32,"Resinee -onon gom…óin…ďe …ďen- …ďen wor…ďe …ďe alah sonnaa…ďe, e …ďen rim…ďe …ďe alaa moodi…ď…ďe, resinee gom…óin…ďe …ďen immorde e maccu…ďe moo…óon …ďen e hor…ďe moo…óon …ďen kadi, si tawii ko …ďe waasu…ďe Alla al…óiniray …ďe ∆Āural Makko yaajungal ngal, Alla ko O Yaaju…óo Arsike, al…óinngol go…ó…óo uytataa Arsike Makko on, ko O Anndu…óo alhaaliiji jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  24,33,"∆Āen …ďe hattanaani resugol sabu baasal ma…ď…ďe, yo …ďe …óa…ď…ďu …ďuurnaade gaa e jina ngon haa Alla al…óinira …ďe ∆Āural Makko Yaajungal ngal. ∆Āen maccu…ďe wonu…ďe …óa…ď…ďude soottaadede ka koohoo…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen e dow yo…ďugol jawdi fii yo …ďe rin…óu, no fawii koohoo…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen ja…ďanngol …ďe …óum, si …ďe anndirii …ďe hattaneede tottugol ngol e mo∆ī∆īugol ka diina, haray no fawii …ďe nde …ďe jonnata …ďe jawdi Alla ndi O jonni …ďe ndin, …óum woni …ďe fukkana …ďe peccun e ko …ďe winndi …ďe kon fii yo…ďugol …óum. Wata on doolu hor…ďe moo…óon …ďen e jeeno fii …óa…ď…ďugol jawdi -wano Abdullaahi bun ubayyu wa…óirnoo non hor…ďe makko …ďen …ói…óo fewndo …ďe …óa…ď…ďunoo nantagol e wo…ó…óitagol e pankare …óen- fii yo on …óa…ď…ďu ko o faggitori kon farju makko on, kala doolu…óo …ďe e moo…óon fii …óum, pellet, Alla …ďaawo doolugol …ďe ngol ko O Surroowo junuubu ma…ď…ďe on, Yurmetee…óo …ďe; sabu ko …ďe doolaa…ďe, bakkaatu on ko fawii ko e doolu…óo …ďe on."
  24,34,"Gom…óii Men tippinii e moo…óon -onon yim…ďe …ďen- Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe jil…ďuya alah e majje, Men tippini e moo…óon misal immorde e …ďen fe∆ī∆īunoo…ďe ado moo…óon immorde e gom…óin…ďe e heefer…ďe, Men tippini e moo…óon waaju …ďen huloo…ďe Joomi mu'un hi…ďe waajitora ngu …óoftagol Yamraa…ói Makko …óin e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin."
  24,35,"Ko Alla woni ndaygu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e fewnoowo …ďen wonu…ďe e majji. Sifa ndaygu Makko ngun ka …ďernde gom…óin…óo on, ko wano tu…ó…óere e maadi ndaynginndi ndi alaa wuddere, hara pitilol no e mayri, pitilol ngol no e nder biiniiri fewtinaandi a wi'ayma ko ndi hoodere jalbunde. Ngol pitilol no hu…ď…ďiniree nebban leggal barkinaangal, ngal le ko leggal nebbantiwal ngal. Huunde heedah ngal leggal e naange ngen, wanaa ka bimmbi wanaa ka kiikii…óe. Nebban maggal …óam no …óa…ďa jalbude sabu laa…ďugol majjam, hay si yiite meemaali …óam. Ko honno kan si yiite meemii …óam? Ndaygu pitilol ngol …ďeydoo e ndaygu biiniiri ndin. Ko nii de …ďernde gom…óin…óo on wa'ata si ndaygu peewal ngal jalbii e mayre. Alla hino hawrinndina e jokkugol Alqur'aana on on mo O muuyi immorde e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Alla no …ďannginira piiji …óin nanndo majji piyirgol …ói mise. Alla ko Anndu…óo kala huunde. Huunde suu…óanaaki Mo."
  24,36,"Ngol pitilol no hu…ď…ďinee e nder Juulir…óe …óe Alla Yamiri mahugol e townugol fii majje, Innde Makko jaŇčtoree e majje Noddinaandu ndun e Julde nden e jaŇčtagol ngol, no juulee e nder majje fii …óa…ď…ďugol welayee Alla ka arannde √Īalal ngal e ka sakkitorde maggal."
  24,37,"Wor…ďe …ďe soodugol e yeeyugol maapintaa …óum gaayi jaŇčtagol Alla Senayee wonanii Mo, e tottirgol Julde nden no haaniri non, e jonnugol Jakka on henndotoo…ďe mo …ďen, hara hi…ďe huli √Ďalnde Darngal, nden √Ďalaande nde waylitoytoo e muu…óum …ďer…óe …óen hakkunde tama'u da…óugol immorde e Lepte …óen e kulol majje, gii…óe …óen waylitoyoo e mayre faade e nokku kala ka …óe yaari."
  24,38,"Ko …ďe golliri …óum ko fii yo Alla yo…ďu …ďe e dow golle ma…ď…ďe …óen ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude ko …ďe gollunoo kon, O …ďeydana …ďe kadi immorde e ∆Āural Makko ngal njo…ďdi e dow mu'un. Alla no arsika on mo O Muuyi ko aldaa e hasboore e dow emmbere golle ma…ď…ďe …óen, ko woni hiMo okka …ďe cowe ko …ďe gollunoo kon."
  24,39,"∆Āen yeddu…ďe Alla, golle ma…ď…ďe …óe …ďe golli …óen, …óe maraa baraaji, ko yeru merere wonnde e hollaande …óon…óaa…óo on no yi'a nde o sikka ko nde ndiyam, o yaha e mayre haa si o hewtii o daroo e hoore mayre o he…ďataa ndiyam, ko wano nii yeddu…óo on himo sikka wonnde golle makko …óen …óe nafay mo, haa si o maayii o immintinaama hara o he…ďatah baraaji golle …óen. O tawa Joomi makko yeeso makko O huu…ďinana mo hasboore golle makko …óen haa timma, Alla ko O Yaawu…óo Hasboore."
  24,40,"Maa…óum golle ma…ď…ďe …óen ko yeru ni…ďe e nder maayo luggungo, no dow maggo benpe∆ī∆īe, no dow …óen benpe∆ī∆īe benpe∆ī∆īe goo, no dow majje duule hi…óe suddi koode tinddinortee…óe …óen, ni…ďe fawondir…óe yoga e majje e dow yoga, si ukkii…óo e …óee ni…ďe …óoo yaltinii junngo mu'un ngon o …ďadotaako yi'ugol ngo sabu sa…ótude ni…ďe …óen, ko wano nii kadi yeddu…óo on, gom…óii fawondirii e hoore makko ni…ďe majjere e sikke e wemmbere e uddeede …ďernde makko, on mo Alla arsikaali Peewal immorde e majjere nden, e ganndal ka Deftere Makko, haray o marah peewal ngal o feewita …óum, wanah kadi deftere nde o ndaygirta …óum."
  24,41,"Kaa a anndaa -an Nulaa…óo- wonndema Alla no subuhinanoo Mo …ďen wonu…ďe ka kammuuli, no subuhinanoo Mo …ďen wonu…ďe ka leydi immorde e tageefooji, colli…óin kadi no subuhinanoo Mo hi…ói fonti gabitanji(bibje) majji ka weeyo? Gootel kala e …óii tageefooji Alla hiMo Annadi Julde kala juulu…óo immorde e majji wano ne…ó…óanke on, e subuhinaali kala subuhinii…óo immorde e majji wano colli …óin, Alla ko O Anndu…óo ko …ďe huuwata, suu…óanaaki Mo hay e huunde e golle ma…ď…ďe …óen."
  24,42,"Ko Alla heeranii kanko tun Laamu kammuuli …óin e Laamu leydi ndin, ko faade ka Makko Kanko tun woni ruttorde √Ďalnde Darngal fii Hasboore e njo…ďdi."
  24,43,"Kaa a anndaa -an Nulaa…óo- wonndema Alla hiMo sogga duulere, refti O hawtindira yoga e cenkoy mayre faade e yoga, refti O wa…óa nde fawondirnde O dewta yoga e mayre e dow yoga, yi'aa to…ďo ngon no yalta ka nder duulere, no iwa ka kammu jippoo immorde e …óen duule sukku…óe nanndu…óe e pelle sabu mawnugol majje, [no yalta ton kadi] kunte ndiyam fenndii…óam wa'u…óam wa koccuuje, O hewtina …óen marmalle on mo O Muuyi immorde jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, O firta …óe e on mo O Muuyi e ma…ď…ďe, ndaygu ma∆īe duule …óen no do'a na…ďude gii…óe …óen sabu sa…ótude jalbugol majje."
  24,44,"Alla hiMo lontindira hakkunde jemma on e √Īalorma on ka juutugol e ka ra…ď…ďi…óugol, e ka yahugol e ka arugol, pellet, no e …óum ko jaŇčtaa …óoo immorde e Aayeeje e daliilaaji joomayankooji waaju tinndin…ói e dow Kattan…óe Alla e Ngootimmbaaku Makko wonannde joomoraa…ďe gii…óe …ďen."
  24,45,"Ko Alla Tagi kala ko woni ladude ka hoore leydi e mummunteeji …óin immorde e to…ď…ďere [maniiyu], no e majji …óin yaarooji reedu muu…óum e daasagol wano mbolle …óen, no e majji …óin yaarooji kay…óe …ói…ói wano ne…ó…óo on e sonndu ndun, no e majji kadi …óin yaarooji [koy…óe] nayi wano neemoraa…ói …óin, Alla hiMo Taga ko O Muuyi ko O jaŇčtii kon e ko O jaŇčtaaki kon kadi, pellet, Alla ko O hattan…óo e dow kala huunde, hay e huunde ronkintah Mo."
  24,46,"Gom…óii Men Tellinii e dow Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe ko jil…ďi alah e majje, Alla hiMo hawrinndina on mo O Muuyi faade e Laawol focciingol, ngol oo√Īannde e muu…óum, ngol Laawol yottina mo ka Aljanna."
  24,47,"Naafiqii…ďe …ďen no wi'a: "Men gom…óinii Alla, men gom…óinii Nulaa…óo on, men …óoftike Alla, men …óoftike Nulaa…óo on kadi, refti fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe huccita, hara …ďe …óoftaaki Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on ka yamaroore fii Jihaadi ka Laawol Alla e tanaa muu…óum …ďaawo …ďe aa∆īike …óum ko e gom…óinal Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on e …óoftagol …ďe kam…ďe …ói…óo, …ďen huccitu…ďe gaayi …óoftagol Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, …ďen wonaali gom…óin…ďe hay si …ďe nodditike wonndema ko …ďe gom…óin…ďe."
  24,48,"Si …ďee naafiqii…ďe …ďen noddaama faade ka Alla, e ka Nulaa…óo on fii yo Nulaa…óo on √Īaawu hakkunde ma…ď…ďe fii ko…ďe wennjondiri e fii mu'un kon, tawa kam…ďe ko …ďe …óuurnii…ďe gaayi √Īaawoore makko nden sabu naafiqaaku ma…ď…ďe ngun."
  24,49,"Si …ďe anndii hi…ďe mari goonga, wonndema o √Īaaway ko nafata…ďe, …ďe aray ka makko ko …ďe …óoftii…ďe yankinii…ďe."
  24,50,"Kaa hara wonu ka …ďer…óe …ďee √Īaw duumiingu e majje, kaa …ďe sikkiti wonnde kanko ko o Nulaa…óo Alla, kaa …ďe hulu wata Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on too√Īu …ďe ka √Īaawoore? Hay e huunde e koo ko jaŇčtaa…óoo wonaali, ko woni, ko sabu √Īaw wonngu ka wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe sabu …óuuragol ma…ď…ďe gaayi √Īaawoore makko nden e sanndalingol nde."
  24,51,"Anndu ko wonata konngol gom…óin…ďe …ďen si …ďe noddaama faade ka Alla e ka Nulaa…óo on fii yo √Īaawu hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ko nde …ďe wi'ata: "Men nanii Daaluyee Makko on, men …óoftike Yamiroore Makko nde." ∆Āen sifor…ďe …óii sifaaji ko kam…ďe woni malaa…ďe …ďen ka aduna e ka Laakara."
  24,52,"Kala …óoftii…óo Alla o …óoftii Nulaa…óo Makko on, o jebbilanii √Īaawoore Ma…ď…ďe nden, o huli ko goopi …óin poo…óata kon, o rentori e Lepte Alla …óen …óoftagol Yamiroore Makko nden, e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, haray …ďen …óon ko kam…ďe tun woni maliraa…ďe mo∆ī∆īere aduna on e Laakara on."
  24,53,"Naafiqii…ďe …ďen woondiri Alla kaddi goondooje ma…ď…ďe tii…óinaa…óe …óen …óe…ďe hattani woondirgol …óum: "Si a yamirii …ďe yaltugol yaha ka Jihaadi ma …ďe yaltu sanne". Maakan …ďe -an Nulaa…óo-: wata on woondu, penaale moo…óon …óen ko anndaa…óe, …óoftaare moo…óon nde aa∆īi…óon nden ko anndaande. Alla ko O Humpitii…óo ko golloton, hay e huunde e golle mo'on …óen suu…óanaaki Mo noone woo no suu…óir…óon …óe."
  24,54,"An Nulaa…óo maakan …ďee naafiqii…ďe: ∆äoftee Alla …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on, ka kene e ka gunndoo, si on huccitii gaayi e ko yamir…óon kon e …óoftagol …ďe kam…ďe …ói…óo; haray anndu ko fawii mo kanko, ko ko o fawaa kon immorde e yottinngol ngol, no fawii on onon kadi ko fawa…óon kon immorde e …óoftagol ngol e gollirgol ko O addi kon, si on …óoftorii mo gollugol ko o yamiri on kon gollugol e accugol ko o ha…ói on kon, on feeway faande e goonga kan, fawaaki Nulaa…óo on si wanaa yottinngol …ďanngungol, fawaaki mo fawugol on e dow peewal ngal, e doolugol on e dow maggal."
  24,55,"Alla Fodii …ďen gom…óin…ďe Mo jeyaa…ďe e moo…óon …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe …óen, nde O wallata …ďe e dow ay…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, o wa…óa …ďe lontii…ďe ka leydi yeru no O wa…óiranoo non …ďen gom…óin…ďe adii…ďe …ďe lontii…ďe e mayri, O Fodi …ďe nde O wa…óata diina ma…ď…ďe ka O weltorani …ďe kan -…óum le ko Diina Lislaamu kan- wee…ďuka Tedduka, O fodi …ďe O wattitanay …ďe …ďaawo kulol ma…ď…ďe ngol hoolaare. Yo …ďe rewam Min tun, wata …ďe sirkanam hay e huunde. Kala yeddu…óo …ďaawo on neema hara …ďen …óon ko kam…ďe woni yaltu…ďe …ďen gaayi …óoftaare Alla."
  24,56,"Tottiree Julde nden no haaniri non, jonnon Jakka jawle moo…óon …óen, …óoftoron kadi Nulaa…óo on gollugol ko o yamiri on kon e accugol ko o ha…ói on kon e muu…óum, jortagol on he…ďay Yurmeende Alla nden."
  24,57,"Wata a sikku -an Nulaa…óo- …ďen yeddu…ďe Alla …ďe laawoto Lam si Mi faalaama jippingol Lepte …óen e ma…ď…ďe, jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden √Ďalnde Darngal ko Jahannama. On mo Jahannama woni wattinirde mu'un pellet, haray wattabde makko nden bonii."
  24,58,"Ko onon yo gom…óin…ďe Alla, …ďe golliri Sari'a mo O wa…óani …ďe on, yo …óa…ď…ďu duŇčayee e moo…óon maccu…ďe moo…óon …ďen e hor…ďe moo…óon …ďen e sukaa…ďe moo…óon rim…ďe …ďen, …ďen …ďe yottaaki duu…ďi kellefuyee e waqtuuji tati: Ko adii Julde Subaka nden, waqtu wattitugol conci waalor…ói …óin e conci gollir…ói …óin, e ka waqtu jolloro tuma …ďortoto …óon conci moo…óon fii …óoykal njolloor, e ka …ďaawo Julde gee∆īe; sabu ko on fewndo …ďortoto…óon conci moo…óon gollir…ói …óin …ďorno…óon conci …óaanor…ói …óin, …óii waqtuuji …óoo tati ko awraaji moo…óon, wata …ďe naatu ka moo…óon e majji si wonaa …ďaawo duŇčayee moo…óon. Bakkaatu fawaaki on fii naatugol ma…ď…ďe hara …ďe cakkitinaaki, bakkaatu fawaaki …ďe ko wonaa e nder …óii…óoo immorde e waqtuuji. kam…ďe ko …ďe heewu…ďe wangagol, yoga e moo…óon kadi no liigoo ka yoga, gasataa ha…óugol …ďe naatugol e kala waqtu si wanaa …ďe duŇčini. Ko wano Alla …ďannginirani on nii √Īaawooje duŇčinagol ngol O …ďannginiranta on Aayeeje tinndin…óe e ko O Sar'inani on kon immorde e √Īaawooje. Alla ko Anndu…óo nafaaji jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen ko O √Ďee√Īu…óo e nder wa…óanngol …ďe ngol √Īaawooje."
  24,59,"Si sukaa…ďe moo…óon yottike duu…ďi kellefuyoo, yo …ďe …óa…ď…ďu yamiroore tuma naatugol ka cuu…ói e waqtuuji …óin fow, yeru ko jaŇčtaa kon e fiyaake maw…ďe …ďen ko adii, wano Alla …ďannginirani on nii √Īaawooje duŇčinagol ngol Alla …ďannginiranta on Aayeeje Makko …óen, Alla ko O Anndu…óo nafaaji jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, √Ďee√Īu…óo e ko O Sar'inani …ďe kon."
  24,60,"E …ďen yummiraa…ďe accu…ďe fiilaade e sowaade sabu nayewu ma…ď…ďe, …ďen …ďe tam∆īinaaki e dewgal bakkaatu fawaaki …ďe si …ďe wallinii conci ma…ď…ďe …óin wano waanaare nden e tiggaare nden, hara …ďe fe√Ī√Īinaali cu…óaari suu…óiinde ndin, ndi Alla yamiri ndin suu…óugol. Ko nde …ďe accata wallinngol …óin conci …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde …ďe diini wallinngol …ói, ka tentinngol fii surragol e nantagol, Alla ko O Nanoowo konngu…ói moo…óon …óin, Anndu…óo golle moo…óon …óen, hay huunde e …óum suu…óanaaki Mo, aray O yo…ďa on e dow majje."
  24,61,"Junuubu fawaaki on bun…óo waasaa…óo gii…óe mu'un; junuubu fawaaki kadi la∆īu…óo on, junuubu fawaaki kadi nawnu…óo on; si …ďe …óalii ko …ďe hattantaake kon daranagol …óum immorde e ko fawii …ďe wa…óugol wano Jihaadi ka Laawol Alla. Junuubu fawaaki on -onon gom…óin…ďe …ďen- fii √Īaamugol ka cuu…ói moo…óon, no jeyaa e majji cuu…ói …ďi…ó…ďe mooaon, wanaa kadi fii √Īaamugol ka cuu…ói baabiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum neeniraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óun musi…ó…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum musi…ó…ďe moo…óon rew…ďe, maa…óum bappiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum yaayiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum kawiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum neeniraa…ďe moo…óon ka dewol, maa…óum cuu…ói …ói halfina…óon reenugol …óin wano aynu…óo awru. Junuu…ďu alaa e √Īaamugol ka cuu…ói yi…ó…ďe moo…óon sabu weleede wonkii makko e …óum, junuubu fawaaki on nde √Īaamoton ko on moo…ďii…ďe maa…óum √Īaamiron gooto-gooto. Si on natay e cuu…ói sifa …óii cuu…ói jaŇčtaa…ói …óoo e tanaa majji haray salminee …ďen wonu…ďe e nder majji …óum woni wi'on: "Kisiyee e mon" Si tawii go…ó…óo alah e nder majji; haray salminee e dow wonkiiji moo…óon, …óum woni wi'on: "Kisiyee e amen e jeyaa…ďe Alla mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen". ∆äum ko hiwraango immorde ka Alla ngo O Sar'inani on barkinaango; sabu ko ngo saakata kon immorde e giggol e woowoniral hakkunde moo…óon, laa…ďungo no laa…ďira sabu maggo wonkii nanu…óo ngo on, ko yeru ngol …ďannginngol aditiingol ka Simoore Alla …ďannginirta Aayeeje jortagol on hakkilanay …óe, gollitiron ko woni kon e nder majje."
  24,62,"Anndu gom…óin…ďe goongu…ďe …ďen ka gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe, ko …ďen woni gom…óin…ďe Alla …ďe gom…óini kadi Nulaa…óo Makko on, si …ďe laatike hi…ďe wondi e Annabiijo on (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) e fiyaake hawtinir…óo …ďe fii nafa Jul…ďe …ďen, …ďe yahatah haa …ďe …óa…ď…ďira mo duŇčayee fii yahugol. Pellet, …ďen …óa…ď…ďiroo…ďe ma -an Nulaa…óo- duŇčayee tuma yahugol ko …ďen …óon gom…óini Alla, …ďe gom…óini Nulaa…óo Makko on e goonga, si …ďe …óa…ď…ďirii ma duŇčayee fii yoga e fiyaake hittu…óo e ma…ď…ďe duŇčano on mo yi…óu…óaa duŇčanaade e ma…ď…ďe, …óa…ď…ďanaa…ďe yawtaneede junubaaji …óin. Pellet, Alla ko O Yawtoowo tububaaji kala tuubu…óo immorde jeyaa…ďe makko …ďen, ko O Yurmetee…óo …ďe."
  24,63,"Teddinee -onon gom…óin…ďe …ďen- Nulaa…óo Alla on, si on nodday mo, wata on noddir mo innde makko nden, yeru: "Ko an Muhammadu" maa…óum innde baaba makko nden, yeru: "Ko an yo ge…óal Abdullahi" Wano yoga e moo…óon wa…óirta non e yoga, kono wi'ee: "Ko an yo Nulaa…óo Alla, ko an yo Annabaajo Alla" Si o noddii on kadi e muraadu kafaandu(renndaandu) wata on wa…óu noddaandu makko ndun wano noddaandu yoga e moo…óon e yoga e muuraa…ói puy…ói, ko woni, yaccinee nootagol ndu. Gom…óii Alla no Anndi …ďen suu…óotoo…ďe yaha hara waynaaki, …ďen wonu…ďe lunndaade yamaruyee Nulaa…óo on yo …ďe rento wata Alla hewtin …ďe jarrabuyeeji e masiibooji, maa…óum O hewtina …ďe Lepte muusu…óe …óe …ďe mu√Ī√Īotaako e hoore mu'un."
  24,64,"Ko non woniri, pellet, ko Alla tun woodani tagude e jeyde e fewjude ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi, hiMo Anndi -onon yim…ďe …ďen- ko wonu…óon kon e mu'un immorde e alhaaliiji, hay huunde e majji suu…óanaaki Mo, √Ďalnde Darngal -tuma …ďe ruttiroytee ka Makko Immital …ďaawo maayde nden- O humpita …ďe ko …ďe gollunoo kon immorde e golle ka aduna, Alla ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde, hay e huunde suu…óanaaki Mo ka kammuuli wanaa ka leydi kadi."
